Diego Maradona to Sue FIFA VP Julio Grondona for ‘Slander,’ Lawyer Says

-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 
2011-05-27T19:19:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/diego-maradona-to-sue-fifa-vp-julio-grondona-for-slander-lawyer-says.html
Diego Maradona  plans to sue FIFA Vice
President Julio Grondona, who also heads  Argentina ’s soccer
association, for “slander,” Maradona’s lawyer Alejandro
Kalbermatten said today in an interview on Buenos Aires-based FM
Identidad Radio. Maradona plans to file lawsuits in Argentina
and abroad, Kalbermatten said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rodrigo Orihuela in  Buenos Aires  at 
 rorihuela@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Robin Saponar at 
 rsaponar@bloomberg.net  